window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The apocalypse is on the horizon, and only one man can stop it.</p> <p>Joined by his Apocalypse Knights, Maximo Strident will face dungeons and monsters at levels never before seen. The worst of all, though, are those deranged parodies of Knights-Errant known as Harbingers.</p> <p>It's a good thing Max can steal spells, because the world depends on him ascending to heights of power once thought impossible.</p>"; 
